QueryToExecute:
select
  arn as resource,
  case
    when vpc_options ->> 'VPCId' is null then 'alarm'
    else 'ok'
  end status,
  case
    when vpc_options ->> 'VPCId' is null then title || ' not in VPC.'
    else title || ' in VPC ' || (vpc_options ->> 'VPCId') || '.'
  end reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_elasticsearch_domain;
